@startuml
autonumber
actor User
participant "Face Detection Module" as FaceDetectionModule
participant "Gesture Recognition Module" as GestureRecognitionModule
participant "Hand Tracking Module" as HandTrackingModule
participant "Interaction Module" as InteractionModule
participant "Real-time Collaboration Module" as RealtimeCollaborationModule
participant "Latency Reduction Module" as LatencyReductionModule
FaceDetectionModule ->> HandTrackingModule : Send face detection data
HandTrackingModule -> GestureRecognitionModule : Trigger gesture recognition
GestureRecognitionModule ->> InteractionModule : Send recognized gesture data
InteractionModule -> RealtimeCollaborationModule : Trigger real-time collaboration
RealtimeCollaborationModule ->> LatencyReductionModule : Send collaboration data
LatencyReductionModule -> RealtimeCollaborationModule : Reflect action on projected surface
@enduml